dataList.content: They made for pathetic foes. Barely counted as a warm-up.

dataList.title: LCCB
dataList.content: The Tingtang Gang practically owned this stretch of the Backstreets. A single battle won't put an end to—
Effie had barely finished speaking when additional Tingtangers began spilling out of the alleyways.

dataList.title: Tingtang Gang
dataList.content: Who sent ya haricots to mess with us on our turf?!
We are the proud soldiers of Limbu―mmph!!
Effie clamped a hand over Don Quixote’s mouth before she could finish.

dataList.title: LCCB
dataList.content: Have you completely lost it? Do you want the entire District coming down on us?!
More incoming! We await your command, Executive Manager!
